SAKURA_MOD_CARD_CLOW_RETURN.description:
[gold]Watery[/gold]
Record the current state and return to this state after {Magic:diff()} rounds.{IfUpgraded:show:| 
Add {Voids:diff()} [gold]Void[/gold] into the discard pile.}

SAKURA_MOD_CARD_CLOW_FLY.description:
[gold]Windy[/gold]
Draw {Cards:diff()} cards. {IfUpgraded:show:|
