SAKURA_MOD_CARD_CLOW_NOTHING.description:
This combat, [gold]Clow Cards[/gold] and [gold]Sakura Cards[/gold] cost 0 and gain Exhaust.
Whenever you play one, gain {Block:diff()} [gold]Block[/gold] and all enemies lose {Damage:diff()} HP. {IfUpgraded:show:|
At the end of combat, randomly remove 1 other card from your deck.}
